Use of Technology
  * As we are starting out as a new company, we will start out by joining with an existing affiliate marketing platform
  * Once we have the financial stabilty, the company will branch out onto our own 
  * By incorporating networks and having various computers, we're able to collect data to help further support our goal
Tools
  * We would have our own database to hold all of the information for the variety of businesses that the company is collaborating with
  * Various departments will have their own systems but still share the same database
  * To keep our website up to date at all times, there will be a specific team to refresh and update the website to ensure that the users
  of the website can get a better variety of recommendations
  * A software would be used to keep track of the activity when users visit our website and see when there is a high and regular amount of activity
  
